40aebf67-eaf3-4e43-a49a-2e939bd23559	How do I book a trip?	Select your trip, click 'Add to Trip' or 'Book Now', and follow the checkout steps. You will receive a confirmation email once payment is complete.	Booking	published	1	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.076463+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.076463+00
f23a9168-b498-481c-8f01-872dbfc4d29c	Can I book for a group?	Yes! During checkout you can specify the number of participants. For groups of 10 or more, contact info@sightseeing.lu for a tailored quote.	Booking	published	2	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.079941+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.079941+00
de488a1a-fcfc-422a-b1a8-28743141f8ab	Do I need an account to book?	No account is required. However, creating one makes it easier to manage bookings and access receipts.	Booking	published	3	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.083207+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.083207+00
e3ccd775-9210-4904-9023-56d248e2b91a	Can I modify my booking after confirming?	Most bookings can be modified up to 24 hours before the experience. Email info@sightseeing.lu with your booking reference.	Booking	published	4	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.093177+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.093177+00
68ad0bd5-a73c-4892-8b30-ff957d6c701b	What payment methods do you accept?	We accept all major credit/debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex) and PayPal. Payments are processed securely via our partner Palisis.	Payments	published	1	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.096066+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.096066+00
ce4b1dd9-de02-4bc9-ba1e-ce5bc9bc563a	Is my payment secure?	Yes. All transactions are processed via PCI-compliant systems. We never store your card details directly.	Payments	published	2	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.100521+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.100521+00
2b80c4f3-fec9-4cb7-bf12-810568e074ee	When is my card charged?	Your card is charged immediately upon booking confirmation.	Payments	published	3	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.103521+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.103521+00
1c09d622-00f8-412d-bbef-7a99f889adf8	Can I pay in instalments?	Currently we do not offer instalment plans. Full payment is required at the time of booking.	Payments	published	4	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.107299+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.107299+00
a1f45073-c30e-466c-a45e-3cfd8b0b2f9a	What is your cancellation policy?	Most experiences offer a full refund if cancelled 24+ hours before start time. Cancellations within 24 hours are generally non-refundable. Each listing shows its specific policy.	Cancellation	published	1	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.110531+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.110531+00
c7c0a3bc-d8f9-4d5f-abfe-edd94cfe4de0	How do I cancel my booking?	Email info@sightseeing.lu with your booking reference and reason. We aim to respond within 2 business hours.	Cancellation	published	2	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.113762+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.113762+00
0fbb9736-552e-44a9-b519-88b3a0b4426a	How long does a refund take?	Refunds are processed within 5-10 business days depending on your bank or card provider.	Cancellation	published	3	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.117235+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.117235+00
5a8ae278-fdcb-4405-9054-cb1e48d9d53d	What if the operator cancels?	You will receive a full refund within 3 business days, or the option to rebook at no extra charge.	Cancellation	published	4	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.120785+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.120785+00
4b99faf6-5236-489a-a768-5ec02f89d15c	Are experiences wheelchair accessible?	Accessibility varies by experience. Each listing includes accessibility notes. Contact us for specific advice.	Accessibility	published	1	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.124256+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.124256+00
4db25a75-33f3-45c6-9239-eec78a500136	Are experiences suitable for young children?	Many are family-friendly. Look for the 'family' tag on listings or contact us for age-specific recommendations.	Accessibility	published	2	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.127368+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.127368+00
18849850-5877-40ac-ae7e-0d6446f5a15f	Where is sightseeing.lu based?	We are based in Luxembourg City and our experiences cover the entire Grand Duchy and some cross-border destinations.	General	published	1	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.130379+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.130379+00
36a5c620-dc57-4b3f-9459-7ab25d50ae0c	How do I contact customer support?	Email info@sightseeing.lu or use the AI chat on this page. We respond within a few hours, Mon-Sat, 9:00-18:00 CET.	General	published	2	\N	\N	2026-04-27 08:46:29.134081+00	2026-04-27 08:46:29.134081+00
