tcms_23	23	Luxembourg City’s Most Instagrammable Spots by Bus	\N	Ready to explore one of Europe’s most beautiful capitals from our touristic minibus? Join this tour and experience the breathtaking views, historic landmarks and hidden gems of Luxembourg City while taking pictures of the city’s most photographed spots	\N	25.00	\N	75 minutes	Tours	{}	Luxembourg	Sightseeing.lu	https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/23/1/large.jpg	{https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/23/1/large.jpg}	{"Admire Luxembourg City's historic center.","Photograph the city's main attractions,","Enjoy this tour in comfort and style"}	\N	0.00	0	https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=23&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=907775fe1710	\N	t	f	published	{"ex": "* Live Guide", "exp": "* Admire Luxembourg City's historic center.\\n* Photograph the city's main attractions,\\n* Enjoy this tour in comfort and style", "inc": "* Minibus tour\\n* Audio guide in 7 languages", "grade": 1, "has_d": 1, "has_f": 0, "has_h": 0, "cutoff": {"type": "before_start_sec", "value": 0}, "images": {"image": [{"url": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/23/1/default.jpg", "image_id": 1, "url_large": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/23/1/large.jpg", "@_thumbnail": "true", "url_thumbnail": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/23/1/thumbnail.jpg"}]}, "inc_ex": "* Minibus tour\\n* Audio guide in 7 languages", "redeem": "* Meeting point: Spuerkeess, 2320 Ville-Haute Luxembourg", "country": "LU", "summary": "Our minibus tour begins in the vibrant city center, on Place de Metz, near the Spuerkeess BCEE building", "tour_id": 23, "book_url": "https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=23&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=907775fe1710", "duration": 1, "end_time": "MULTI", "has_sale": 1, "location": "Luxembourg", "longdesc": "Ready to explore one of Europe’s most beautiful capitals from our touristic minibus? Join this new tour and experience the breathtaking views, historic landmarks and hidden gems of Luxembourg City while taking pictures of the city’s most photographed spots.\\n\\nOur journey begins in the vibrant city center, on Place de Metz. Here you will already admire the Spuerkeess building, one of the oldest symbols of architecture in the city.\\nYour driver will take you through the lively Gare Centrale district, a multicultural and dynamic area that showcases another authentic side of the city.\\n\\nThen, travel through the historic heart of the city, including the UNESCO-listed Old Town and the impressive Bock Casemates, carved into the rock and full of fascinating history.\\nYou will be able to get out of the bus for a few minutes to admire and photograph the spectacular panorama from the Chemin de la Corniche, often called as Europe’s most beautiful balcony.\\n\\nDiscover the modern business and artistic district of Luxembourg in the Kirchberg district, where you will admire the fascinating architecture of the MUDAM (Museum of Modern Art Grand-Duc Jean) and the breathtaking Philharmonie of Luxembourg. Don’t miss the opportunity to photograph both outstanding infrastructures. Around the area, you will have the chance to admire the great city panoramic view behind the Fort Thüngen built in 1732- another great photography spot.\\n\\nFrom historic fortifications to contemporary landmarks, from panoramic views to vibrant streets – this Instagram tour offers a complete overview of Luxembourg City in comfort and style. An ideal activity for first-time visitors, families, friends or couples wishing to discover Luxembourg from a new perspective!", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/luxembourg-city-highlights-instagram-tour-by-minibus/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "Check availability Calendar", "documents": "", "essential": "* This tour is 75 minutes long. \\n* This Tour is not a Hop on Hop off", "shortdesc": "Ready to explore one of Europe’s most beautiful capitals from our touristic minibus? Join this tour and experience the breathtaking views, historic landmarks and hidden gems of Luxembourg City while taking pictures of the city’s most photographed spots", "time_type": "strict", "tour_name": "Luxembourg City’s Most Instagrammable Spots by Bus", "tour_tags": {"tag": [{"text": "Activity is suitable for adults only", "token": "adults-only", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around animals", "token": "animals", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour is guided by pre-recorded commentary", "token": "audio-guide", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity visits or happens at a beach", "token": "beaches", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour involves sightseeing by bicycle", "token": "bike-tours", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour involves sightseeing by boat", "token": "boat-tours", "value": 0}, {"text": "Card or pass that offers admission to multiple top attractions", "token": "city-cards", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is conducted in a class or workshop setting", "token": "classes", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is a full-day or multi-day trip", "token": "day-trips", "value": 1}, {"text": "Activity is suitable for adults and children of all ages", "token": "family-friendly", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity includes skip-the-line admission", "token": "fast-track", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around food", "token": "food", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is history-related or happens in a historical location", "token": "history", "value": 0}, {"text": "Hop-on hop-off tour by bus, boat, etc", "token": "hop-on-hop-off", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around a literature theme", "token": "literature", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity includes a live music performance", "token": "live-music", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity visits or happens at a museum", "token": "museums", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity includes social activities or entertainment at night", "token": "nightlife", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity happens outside or in nature", "token":