Luxembourg, Spuerkeess	49.607646,6.128557	Luxembourg, Spuerkeess	49.607646,6.128557	LU	MEDIUM	Immerse yourself in the enchanting beauty of Luxembourg with our enchanting Nature and Castles Day Tour through Luxembourg. This captivating experience combines the breathtaking landscapes of the countryside with the rich history and grandeur of Luxembourg’s regions	Embark on a journey through lush green valleys, meandering rivers, and picturesque forests that showcase Luxembourg’s natural wonders. Witness the harmonious coexistence of nature and architecture as you explore stunning castles nestled within this idyllic setting. Our friendly driver will gladly drive you throughout the scenic landscapes of our beautiful country.\n\nWith the help of the informative audio guides in the bus, learn about the remarkable stories of the past that have shaped the region into what it is today. Indulge your senses as you step into centuries-old castles (Beaufort and Vianden) filled with opulent interiors, intricate details, and breathtaking views. Imagine yourself transported back in time as you stroll through elegant halls, marvel at stunning artwork, and discover hidden treasures within these architectural marvels. Throughout the tour, you’ll have ample opportunities to capture unforgettable moments amidst the stunning natural landscapes and breathtaking castle backdrops. Whether you’re a history enthusiast, nature lover, or simply seeking a day of exploration and relaxation, this spectacular sightseeing visit promises a truly unforgettable experience.  \n\nSo, embark on this captivating journey and let us take you on a magical adventure through the heart of Luxembourg’s captivating nature and majestic castles. Book your Nature and Castle Day Tour soon and discover the beauty and charm that awaits you in this exceptional destination	* Learn more about Luxembourg's nature and history\n* Explore the Mullerthal trail and the Schiessentümpel waterfall\n* Visit the city of Vianden and its medieval castle\n* Discover the old town of Echternach	{"8-hour tour","Audio Guide in 3 languages (EN, FR, DE)","Fixed schedule with visits to the Schiessentümpel waterfall","Entry ticket to the castle in Vianden (not guided)"}	{Lunch,Drinks}	* Please note the the Beaufort Castle remains closed from November until end of March	\N	\N	\N	\N	10:00 – 10:45: Mullerthal trail and Schiessentümpel waterfall\nThe waterfall, known as Schiessentümpel, with its three water jets on the Black Ernz is one of the most photographed motives of the Mullerthal Region, Luxembourg’s Little Switzerland. This is a 45-minute walking tour. Please make sure to wear comfortable hiking shoes, especially at the Schiessentümpel waterfall.\n\n11:00: Beaufort Castle (Closed from November until March)\nOne stop at Beaufort to take some photos and admire the view. During Spring and Summer season, the Beaufort Castle is open to the public.\n\n 12:00 – 14:00: Vianden Castle – An outstanding monument\nThe small medieval town of Vianden attracts thousands of visitors every year. Particularly worth seeing are the imposing castle that overlooks the town, the town wall with its fortified towers and Luxembourg’s only chairlift. During our stop you have 2 hours of free time that you can plan for yourself. We recommend that you bring a lunch or snack if you don’t want to waste time in a restaurant, otherwise the time might be too short.\n\n 15:15 – 16:00: The old town of Echternach\nEchternach is the oldest town in Luxembourg and was founded in 698 by the Benedictine monk Willibrord. Visit the most beautiful places and buildings of Echternach, like the Basilica, the abbey and the market. After Echternach, we will return to the departure point in Luxembourg City	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	10	f	2026-05-22	2026-12-19
tcms_15	15	Gourmet journey aboard the Dinner Hopping Bus	\N	Embark on a delectable gourmet Dinner Hopping experience in Luxembourg. Uncover the hidden gems of gourmet delights with this gastronomical tour powered by sightseeing.lu	\N	109.00	\N	4 hours	Tours	{}	Luxembourg	Sightseeing.lu	https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/15/1/large.png	{https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/15/1/large.png}	{"Surprise menu served in a transformed retro American School Bus.","Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening.","Exclusive concept in Luxembourg.","Playlist on board to create a chill-out ambience.","VIP table for 2 people, with a complimentary bottle of crémant"}	\N	0.00	0	https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=15&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=288061e2636c	\N	f	f	published	{"ex": "* Drinks\\n* Guide", "exp": "* Surprise menu served in a transformed retro American School Bus.\\n* Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening.\\n* Exclusive concept in Luxembourg.\\n* Playlist on board to create a chill-out ambience.\\n* VIP table for 2 people, with a complimentary bottle of crémant", "inc": "* 4-hour journey\\n* Service on board of the bus\\n* Surprise 3-course-menu", "grade": 1, "has_d": 1, "has_f": 0, "has_h": 0, "cutoff": {"type": "before_start_sec", "value": 0}, "images": {"image": [{"url": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/15/1/default.png", "image_id": 1, "url_large": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/15/1/large.png", "@_thumbnail": "true", "url_thumbnail": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/15/1/thumbnail.png"}]}, "inc_ex": "* 4-hour journey\\n* Service on board of the bus\\n* Surprise 3-course-menu", "redeem": "* Meeting Point: P+R Bouillon, Rue de Bouillon, 1248 Hollerich Luxembourg, Luxembourg\\n* Please be at the meeting point 10 minutes before departure", "country": "LU", "summary": "Gourmet dinner hopping experience in Luxembourg", "tour_id": 15, "book_url": "https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=15&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=288061e2636c", "duration": 1, "end_time": "MULTI", "has_sale": 1, "location": "Luxembourg", "longdesc": "<strong>The concept of Dinner Hopping</strong>\\nThe Dinner Hopping concept revolves around the notion of transitioning between different restaurants, allowing participants to savor a diverse range of meals while traversing Luxembourg’s stunning streets and views. The restaurant’s dedicated staff will serve a 3-course menu aboard the bus. During a 20 to 30-minute break, passengers have the option to disembark, enjoy some fresh air or utilize the restaurant’s facilities.  \\n\\n<strong>Gourmet Tour</strong>\\nThis Gourmet Tour in Luxembourg is a one-of-a-kind experience that promises to tantalize your taste buds and ignite your sense of adventure. This extraordinary culinary journey is perfect for travelers, foodies, or anyone seeking a fun evening filled with delectable delights. Embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other as you venture through the vibrant streets of our city, discovering hidden culinary gems and savoring exquisite dishes from top-rated restaurants. Immerse yourself in the local food culture as our knowledgeable staff lead you from one culinary hot-spot to another, revealing the secrets behind each carefully crafted dish.\\n\\nIndulge in a multi-course extravaganza, where each course is carefully curated to showcase the diverse flavors and culinary expertise of our city’s finest chefs. From mouthwatering starters that tease your palate to sumptuous main courses that leave you longing for more, each dish is a work of art that tells a story of culinary passion and innovation. Along the way, engage with fellow food enthusiasts, sharing stories, laughter, and a genuine love for the culinary arts.\\n\\nThis interactive experience not only satisfies your taste buds but also provides an opportunity to connect with like-minded individuals, creating memories and friendships that will last long after the tour ends.\\n\\nThis Gourmet Tour experience on the American School Bus takes you on a memorable journey through our city’s culinary landscape, celebrating the flavors, traditions, and creativity of our local food scene. From trendy eateries to hidden gems, each stop on the tour offers a unique foodie experience that will leave you craving for more.\\n\\nSo, if you’re ready to embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other, join us for the Gourmet Tour in Luxembourg. Get ready to indulge in a feast for the senses, discover new flavors, and create unforgettable memories. Book your spot now and get ready to be captivated by the culinary magic that awaits you!", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/gourmet-food-journey-on-the-dinner-hopping-bus/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "Check Availability Calendar", "documents": "", "essential": "*  We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or a voucher.\\n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may be at adjacent tables.\\n* With a VIP ticket, we guarantee you an exclusive table. Sit exclusively with your partner or group at a table without other guests. VIP table per person ( 10,00€).\\n* For VIP Ticket: a bottle of crémant is included.\\n*  No cash payment on board accepted. \\n* Please be at the meeting point 10 minutes before departure", "shortdesc": "Embark on a delectable gourmet Dinner Hopping experience in Luxembourg. Uncover the hidden gems of gourmet delights with this gastronomical tour powered by sightseeing.lu", "time_type": "strict", "tour_name": "Gourmet journey aboard the Dinner Hopping Bus", "tour_tags": {"tag": [{"text": "Activity is suitable for adults only", "token": "adults-only", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around animals", "token": "animals", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tou