: 0, "distribution_identifier": "SI_12846_15", "suitable_for_wheelchairs": 0, "tour_departure_structure": {"type": "SINGLE", "start_times": {"time": "19:15"}, "add_new_auto": 1, "departure_types": ""}, "descriptions_last_updated": "2026-05-19"}	2026-05-22 07:25:14.889+00	palisis	\N	\N	2026-05-12 12:31:19.863842+00	2026-05-22 07:25:14.890041+00	Other	9	Guided (tour guide / driver)	All ages / Not applicable	No accommodation / Not applicable	{food,operator-direct-product}	{en,fr,de}	P+R Bouillon	49.599662,6.107884	P+R Bouillon	49.599662,6.107884	LU	MEDIUM	Embark on a delectable gourmet Dinner Hopping experience in Luxembourg. Uncover the hidden gems of gourmet delights with this gastronomical tour powered by sightseeing.lu	<strong>The concept of Dinner Hopping</strong>\nThe Dinner Hopping concept revolves around the notion of transitioning between different restaurants, allowing participants to savor a diverse range of meals while traversing Luxembourg’s stunning streets and views. The restaurant’s dedicated staff will serve a 3-course menu aboard the bus. During a 20 to 30-minute break, passengers have the option to disembark, enjoy some fresh air or utilize the restaurant’s facilities.  \n\n<strong>Gourmet Tour</strong>\nThis Gourmet Tour in Luxembourg is a one-of-a-kind experience that promises to tantalize your taste buds and ignite your sense of adventure. This extraordinary culinary journey is perfect for travelers, foodies, or anyone seeking a fun evening filled with delectable delights. Embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other as you venture through the vibrant streets of our city, discovering hidden culinary gems and savoring exquisite dishes from top-rated restaurants. Immerse yourself in the local food culture as our knowledgeable staff lead you from one culinary hot-spot to another, revealing the secrets behind each carefully crafted dish.\n\nIndulge in a multi-course extravaganza, where each course is carefully curated to showcase the diverse flavors and culinary expertise of our city’s finest chefs. From mouthwatering starters that tease your palate to sumptuous main courses that leave you longing for more, each dish is a work of art that tells a story of culinary passion and innovation. Along the way, engage with fellow food enthusiasts, sharing stories, laughter, and a genuine love for the culinary arts.\n\nThis interactive experience not only satisfies your taste buds but also provides an opportunity to connect with like-minded individuals, creating memories and friendships that will last long after the tour ends.\n\nThis Gourmet Tour experience on the American School Bus takes you on a memorable journey through our city’s culinary landscape, celebrating the flavors, traditions, and creativity of our local food scene. From trendy eateries to hidden gems, each stop on the tour offers a unique foodie experience that will leave you craving for more.\n\nSo, if you’re ready to embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other, join us for the Gourmet Tour in Luxembourg. Get ready to indulge in a feast for the senses, discover new flavors, and create unforgettable memories. Book your spot now and get ready to be captivated by the culinary magic that awaits you!	* Surprise menu served in a transformed retro American School Bus.\n* Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening.\n* Exclusive concept in Luxembourg.\n* Playlist on board to create a chill-out ambience.\n* VIP table for 2 people, with a complimentary bottle of crémant	{"4-hour journey","Service on board of the bus","Surprise 3-course-menu"}	{Drinks,Guide}	*  We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or a voucher.\n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may be at adjacent tables.\n* With a VIP ticket, we guarantee you an exclusive table. Sit exclusively with your partner or group at a table without other guests. VIP table per person ( 10,00€).\n* For VIP Ticket: a bottle of crémant is included.\n*  No cash payment on board accepted. \n* Please be at the meeting point 10 minutes before departure	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	10	f	2026-05-28	2026-11-26
