 city at your pace with our premium e-bike rental service.\\nCruise through the charming streets, effortlessly gliding uphill and taking in the picturesque sights around you. With our top-notch E-bikes, you’ll experience the perfect blend of convenience and adventure, making your journey through the city an unforgettable one.  \\n\\nRent your e-bike with sightseeing.lu:\\nRenting an e-bike with sightseeing.lu offers a convenient and eco-friendly way to explore the city’s sights. With an e-bike rental, you can effortlessly navigate through the city’s hilly terrain and reach popular landmarks quickly. Ride along the designated bike paths, observe  popular  landmarks like the Casemates du Bock and the Notre-Dame Cathedral, and enjoy the scenic views of Luxembourg City!\\n\\n To conclude, Luxembourg City boasts several landmarks and UNESCO world heritage sites that offer a glimpse into rich history and cultural significance. From the well-preserved fortifications to the architectural wonders and vibrant squares, these sites are a testament to the city’s past and present. Exploring all these lovely places and green parks in Luxembourg City is a truly enriching experience for any visitor.  \\n\\n Whether you’d like to ride in the city or in nature, our e-bikes are perfect to escape everyday life, whether alone or in good company. Luxembourg offers a multitude of cycling paths in the city center or on public parks. Don’t hesitate to contact us for advice during the booking procedure. You can also find more information about the guided e-Bike tours on www.sightseeing.lu", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/discover-the-charm-of-luxembourg-on-1-day-e-bike-rentals/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "Check Availability Calendar", "documents": "", "essential": "* If you booked the full-day rental, we ask you to bring the e-bikes before 17:00 (5 pm)", "shortdesc": "Explore the vibrant 