 The concept of our Dinner Hopping is built on the idea of moving from one restaurant to the next, to enjoy a variety of meals while passing the most beautiful streets of Luxembourg. Your 3-course-menu will be served by the restaurant’s own staff inside the bus. The Dinner Hopping bus has also a bar inside and completely renovated seats in order to to ensure passenger comfort.  \\n\\nDuring a 30-minutes break, you can climb off the bus if you wish to get some fresh air or use the restaurant’s restroom facilities. Italian food is more than just pizza and spaghetti. There’s a wide range of ingredients, flavors, and dishes to experiment with. Our partner-restaurants use traditional and fresh ingredients to create innovative dishes that will make you feel like you’ve just arrived in beautiful Tuscany.\\n\\n<strong>Choose your dish:</strong>\\n\\n<strong>Starter:</strong> (Choose one)\\n- Tagliere di Angelo (Italian cold cuts, sun-dried tomatoes, caramelized onions and olives)\\n- Parmigiana (Eggplant parmigiana with tomato sauce and mozzarella)  \\n\\n <strong>Main course:</strong> (Choose one)\\n- Tagliata di manzo with rocket and parmesan\\n- Risotto with porcini mushrooms\\n- Baccalà alla Livornese (Oven-baked cod with potatoes and tomato sauce)\\n- Spaghetti frutti di mare (Spaghetti with seafood)  \\n\\n<strong>Dessert:</strong> (Choose one)\\n- Tiramisu\\n- Pannacotta with red fruits\\n- Chocolate fondant", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/taste-italian-flavors-on-the-dinner-hopping-bus/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "check timetable", "documents": "", "essential": "* We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or refund. \\n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may b