use the restaurant’s restroom facilities. Italian food is more than just pizza and spaghetti. There’s a wide range of ingredients, flavors, and dishes to experiment with. Our partner-restaurants use traditional and fresh ingredients to create innovative dishes that will make you feel like you’ve just arrived in beautiful Tuscany.\n\n<strong>Choose your dish:</strong>\n\n<strong>Starter:</strong> (Choose one)\n- Tagliere di Angelo (Italian cold cuts, sun-dried tomatoes, caramelized onions and olives)\n- Parmigiana (Eggplant parmigiana with tomato sauce and mozzarella)  \n\n <strong>Main course:</strong> (Choose one)\n- Tagliata di manzo with rocket and parmesan\n- Risotto with porcini mushrooms\n- Baccalà alla Livornese (Oven-baked cod with potatoes and tomato sauce)\n- Spaghetti frutti di mare (Spaghetti with seafood)  \n\n<strong>Dessert:</strong> (Choose one)\n- Tiramisu\n- Pannacotta with red fruits\n- Chocolate fondant	* The best of Italian cuisine over a 3-course menu\n* Discover 3 different restaurants in only one evening\n* Explore Luxembourg on board of a 'restaurant on wheels'\n* Hit the road on board of a retro American School Bus (Dinner Hooping)	{"4-hour trip","Service on board",3-course-menu}	{Drinks,"Live Guide"}	* We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or refund. \n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may be at adjacent tables. \n* With a VIP ticket, we guarantee you an exclusive table. Sit exclusively with your partner or group at a table without other guests. VIP table per person (+10,00€). \n* No cash payment on board accepted. \n* Please arrive 10 minutes before departure	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	10	f	2026-05-29	2026-11-28
tcms_8	8	3-hour Food Tour: Uncover the Tastes of Luxembourg	\N	Stroll through the heart of the vibrant Luxembourg City, indulging in a culinary adventure that will awaken your taste buds and immerse in the local culture	\N	90.00	\N	3 hours	Tours	{}	Luxembourg	Sightseeing.lu	https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/8/1/large.jpg	{https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/8/1/large.jpg}	{"Combine a walking tour together with a gastronomic experience","Taste the best of Luxembourgish food","Discover regional food at local shops"}	\N	0.00	0	https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=8&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=e0e964780652	\N	f	f	published	{"ex": "* Drinks (at the customer’s expense)\\n* Additional food", "exp": "* Combine a walking tour together with a gastronomic experience\\n* Taste the best of Luxembourgish food\\n* Discover regional food at local shops", "inc": "* Professional guide \\n* Guided visit of 3 hours \\n* 5 tasting stops \\n* Food tasting at local shops", "grade": 1, "has_d": 1, "has_f": 0, "has_h": 0, "cutoff": {"type": "before_start_sec", "value": 720}, "images": {"image": [{"url": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/8/1/default.jpg", "image_id": 1, "url_large": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/8/1/large.jpg", "@_thumbnail": "true", "url_thumbnail": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/8/1/thumbnail.jpg"}]}, "inc_ex": "* Professional guide \\n* Guided visit of 3 hours \\n* 5 tasting stops \\n* Food tasting at local shops", "redeem": "* This tour is guided in English. Other languages are only on demand. \\n* Meet your guide at the Place de Paris, in front of Coffee Fellows. \\n* Your guide will be wearing a sightseeing.lu shirt opr jacket, or holding a green sightseeing.lu flag. \\n* The tour takes place with a min. number of 3 participants. Under that number, we reserve the right to cancel the booking and refund the client. \\n* If you wish to have this Food Tour in a different language or organize a private tour, get in touch with us at hello@sightseeing.lu", "country": "