tcms_14	14	BBQ  Flavors on the Dinner Hopping Bus	\N	With sightseeing.lu, it also means there’s joy in the kitchen. You will travel through the flavours and aromas of colourful cuisines. Get your taste buds ready for some BBQ and Cajun spiced food are guaranteed!	\N	99.00	\N	4 hours	Tours	{}	Luxembourg	Sightseeing.lu	https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/xlarge.jpg	{https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/xlarge.jpg}	{"Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening","Travel through the streets of Luxembourg aboard our original American school bus","Exclusive dinner concept in Luxembourg","Unique and authentic experience"}	\N	0.00	0	https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=14&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=9aa605b12a97	\N	f	f	published	{"ex": "* Guide on board,\\n* Drinks (during booking)", "exp": "* Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening\\n* Travel through the streets of Luxembourg aboard our original American school bus\\n* Exclusive dinner concept in Luxembourg\\n* Unique and authentic experience", "inc": "* 4-hour tour Service on board \\n* Driver on board \\n* American themed 3-course-menu", "grade": 1, "has_d": 1, "has_f": 0, "has_h": 0, "cutoff": {"type": "before_start_sec", "value": 0}, "images": {"image": [{"url": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/default.jpg", "image_id": 1, "url_large": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/large.jpg", "image_desc": "Route_Image", "url_xlarge": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/xlarge.jpg", "@_thumbnail": "true", "url_thumbnail": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/14/1/thumbnail.jpg"}]}, "inc_ex": "* 4-hour tour Service on board \\n* Driver on board \\n* American themed 3-course-menu", "redeem": "* Meeting Point: Rue de Bouillon, 1248 Hollerich, Luxemburg\\n* Please arrive 10 minutes before departure", "country": "LU", "summary": "BBQ and Cajun flavours food experience tour", "tour_id": 14, "book_url": "https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=14&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=9aa605b12a97", "duration": 1, "end_time": "MULTI", "has_sale": 1, "location": "Luxembourg", "longdesc": "Experience the ultimate BBQ flavors in Luxembourg with our Dinner Hopping adventure!  Indulge in a mouthwatering culinary  journey that showcases their diverse flavors and iconic dishes of American cuisine. From savoring juicy burgers and delectable BBQ such as spare ribs to devouring irresistible brownies and fluffy pancakes, this tour will satisfy your foodie cravings and transport you to the heart of  the American cuisine. Hop on board our  School Bus and embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other!\\n\\n<strong>Dinner Hopping Experience</strong>\\nIn our unique American School Bus, aka Dinner Hopping that we transformed into a restaurant on wheels, you are going to meet other customers of every age, some in pairs, others in groups or individual. The atmosphere becomes lively as soon as the bus’s big hand brake is released: the departure is approaching!  The concept of Dinner Hopping is built on the idea of moving from one restaurant to the next, to enjoy a variety of meals while passing the most beautiful streets of Luxembourg. Your 3-course-menu will be served by the restaurant’s own staff inside the bus. During our 20-30 minute break, you can leave the bus if you want, to get some fresh air or to use the restaurant’s bathroom.\\n\\n<strong>American Food / BBQ</strong>\\nHow about some delicious Spare Ribs, spicy chicken or a juicy Black Angus Burger? The BBQ Tour allows you to flavor authentic North-American cuisine by starting with a small starter cooked by our partner Qosqo, followed by a spectacular dish perfected by the Big Beer Company and to finish off with a yummy dessert created by Memphis Diner. In addition to this culinary journey, enjoy this sightseeing tour and admire the evening views from the bus’s wide windows.\\n\\n<strong>Choose your starter, main dish and dessert from the menu below:</strong>\\n<strong>Starter:</strong>\\n- Tuna Empanadas\\n- Croquetas with cheddar & jalapeños (veggie)\\n- Patatas bravas with aioli sauce and pico (veggie)\\n\\n<strong>Main Course:</strong>\\n- Beef burger with cheddar, iceberg, bacon and homemade French fries\\n- Vegan burger with grilled vegetables, green salad, tomato salad and hash browns\\n- Spare ribs 400 g (with twister fries and mixed salad)\\n- Spicy chicken (with fries and mixed salad)\\n\\n<strong>Dessert:</strong>\\n- Chocolate Brownie\\n- Fluffy pancakes with maple syrup\\n- Churros", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/bbq-flavors-on-the-dinner-hopping-bus/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "Check Availability Calendar", "documents": "", "essential": "* We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or refund.  \\n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may be at adjacent tables.  \\n* With a VIP ticket, we guarantee you an exclusive table.  VIP table: Sit exclusively with your partner or group at a table without other guests.\\n* VIP table per person (+10,00€). \\n* No cash payment on board accepted.  \\n* Please arrive 10 minutes before departure", "shortdesc": "With sightseeing.lu, it also means there’s joy in the kitchen. You will travel through the flavours and aromas of colourful cuisines. Get your taste buds ready for some BBQ and Cajun spiced food are guaranteed!", "time_type": "strict", "tour_name": "BBQ Flavors on the Dinner Hopping Bus", "tour_tags": {"tag": [{"text": "Activity is suitable for adults only", "token": "adults-only", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around animals", "token": "animals", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour is guided by pre-recorded commentary", "token": "audio-guide", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity visits or happens at a beach", "token": "beach