hout experience"}, {"name": "regularly_sanitized", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Regularly sanitized high-traffic areas"}, {"name": "equipment_sanitized", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Gear/equipment sanitized between use"}, {"name": "transportation_vehicles_sanitized", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Transportation vehicles regularly sanitized"}, {"name": "guides_required_to_wash_hands", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Guides required to wash hands"}, {"name": "temperature_checks_for_staff", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Regular temperature checks for staff"}, {"name": "temperature_checks_for_travelers", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Temperature checks for travelers upon arrival"}, {"name": "contactless_payments_for_extras", "value": "NOTSET", "display_name": "Contactless payments for gratuities and add-ons"}]}, "pickup_on_request": 0, "redemption_method": "", "suitable_for_solo": 0, "from_price_display": "&#8364;99", "last_bookable_date": "2026-11-25", "next_bookable_date": "2026-05-30", "supplier_tour_code": "PALISIS_55_11949", "cancellation_policy": "", "geocode_start_point": {"label": "P+R Bouillon", "geocode": "49.599662,6.107884", "loc_relation": 0, "google_place_id": "ChIJG7sSDwBJlUcR2Nj--m144AE"}, "suitable_for_groups": 0, "suitable_for_couples": 0, "suitable_for_business": 0, "suitable_for_children": 0, "suitable_for_students": 0, "default_departure_size": 20, "from_price_apr_display": "&#8364;0", "from_price_aug_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_dec_display": "&#8364;0", "from_price_feb_display": "&#8364;0", "from_price_jan_display": "&#8364;0", "from_price_jul_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_jun_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_mar_display": "&#8364;0", "from_price_may_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_nov_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_oct_display": "&#8364;99", "from_price_sep_display": "&#8364;99", "tour_permit_child_only": 0, "distribution_identifier": "SI_12846_14", "suitable_for_wheelchairs": 0, "tour_departure_structure": {"type": "NOTSET"}, "descriptions_last_updated": "2026-05-19"}	2026-05-22 07:25:17.461+00	palisis	\N	\N	2026-05-12 12:31:17.879313+00	2026-05-22 07:25:17.462328+00	Other	9	Guided (tour guide / driver)	All ages / Not applicable	No accommodation / Not applicable	{food,operator-direct-product}	{en,fr,de}	P+R Bouillon	49.599662,6.107884	P+R Bouillon	49.599662,6.107884	LU	MEDIUM	With sightseeing.lu, it also means there’s joy in the kitchen. You will travel through the flavours and aromas of colourful cuisines. Get your taste buds ready for some BBQ and Cajun spiced food are guaranteed!	Experience the ultimate BBQ flavors in Luxembourg with our Dinner Hopping adventure!  Indulge in a mouthwatering culinary  journey that showcases their diverse flavors and iconic dishes of American cuisine. From savoring juicy burgers and delectable BBQ such as spare ribs to devouring irresistible brownies and fluffy pancakes, this tour will satisfy your foodie cravings and transport you to the heart of  the American cuisine. Hop on board our  School Bus and embark on a gastronomic adventure like no other!\n\n<strong>Dinner Hopping Experience</strong>\nIn our unique American School Bus, aka Dinner Hopping that we transformed into a restaurant on wheels, you are going to meet other customers of every age, some in pairs, others in groups or individual. The atmosphere becomes lively as soon as the bus’s big hand brake is released: the departure is approaching!  The concept of Dinner Hopping is built on the idea of moving from one restaurant to the next, to enjoy a variety of meals while passing the most beautiful streets of Luxembourg. Your 3-course-menu will be served by the restaurant’s own staff inside the bus. During our 20-30 minute break, you can leave the bus if you want, to get some fresh air or to use the restaurant’s bathroom.\n\n<strong>American Food / BBQ</strong>\nHow about some delicious Spare Ribs, spicy chicken or a juicy Black Angus Burger? The BBQ Tour allows you to flavor authentic North-American cuisine by starting with a small starter cooked by our partner Qosqo, followed by a spectacular dish perfected by the Big Beer Company and to finish off with a yummy dessert created by Memphis Diner. In addition to this culinary journey, enjoy this sightseeing tour and admire the evening views from the bus’s wide windows.\n\n<strong>Choose your starter, main dish and dessert from the menu below:</strong>\n<strong>Starter:</strong>\n- Tuna Empanadas\n- Croquetas with cheddar & jalapeños (veggie)\n- Patatas bravas with aioli sauce and pico (veggie)\n\n<strong>Main Course:</strong>\n- Beef burger with cheddar, iceberg, bacon and homemade French fries\n- Vegan burger with grilled vegetables, green salad, tomato salad and hash browns\n- Spare ribs 400 g (with twister fries and mixed salad)\n- Spicy chicken (with fries and mixed salad)\n\n<strong>Dessert:</strong>\n- Chocolate Brownie\n- Fluffy pancakes with maple syrup\n- Churros	* Discover 3 different restaurants in one evening\n* Travel through the streets of Luxembourg aboard our original American school bus\n* Exclusive dinner concept in Luxembourg\n* Unique and authentic experience	{"4-hour tour Service on board","Driver on board","American themed 3-course-menu"}	{"Guide on board,","Drinks (during booking)"}	* We need a min. number of participants for the tour to take place. Otherwise, we reserve the right to cancel the tour and proceed to a re-booking or refund.  \n* Seating arrangements are made by the bus crew. Couples and groups are always seated together – depending on the size of the group, this may be at adjacent tables.  \n* With a VIP ticket, we guarantee you an exclusive table.  VIP table: Sit exclusively with your partner or group at a table without other guests.\n* VIP table per person (+10,00€). \n* No cash payment on board accepted.  \n* Please arrive 10 minutes before departure	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	10	f	2026-05-30	2026-11-25
tcms_2	2	Luxembourg City Tour	\N	Immerse into the beauty of Luxembourg’s capital city and explore the hidden gems on board of our sightseeing cozy minibus. Listen to an audio guide and admire the historic landmarks and architecture as well as the vibrant and modern side of the city	\N	25.00	\N	75 min	Tours	{}	Luxembourg	Sightseeing.lu	https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/2/1/large.jpg	{https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/2/1/large.jpg}	{"Embark on a sightseeing tour through Luxembourg city.","Listen to commentary from the audio guide and learn about the city's history.","Blend into a mix of old and new architecture.","Explore the vibrant area and unveil hidden gems"}	\N	0.00	0	https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=2&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=e43ff2cdb3ed	\N	f	f	published	{"ex": "* Live Guide", "exp": "* Embark on a sightseeing tour through Luxembourg city.\\n* Listen to commentary from the audio guide and learn about the city's history.\\n* Blend into a mix of old and new architecture.\\n* Explore the vibrant area and unveil hidden gems", "inc": "* Audio guide (5 languages)\\n* Headphones", "grade": 1, "has_d": 1, "has_f": 0, "has_h": 0, "cutoff": {"type": "before_start_sec", "value": 720}, "images": {"image": [{"url": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/2/1/default.jpg", "image_id": 1, "url_large": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/2/1/large.jpg", "@_thumbnail": "true", "url_thumbnail": "https://cdn.tourcms.com/a/12846/2/1/thumbnail.jpg"}]}, "inc_ex": "* Audio guide (5 languages)\\n* Headphones", "redeem": "* Departure Point: Luxembourg, Spuerkeess, Ville Haute Luxembourg\\n* Nearest Train Station:Tram: Place de Metz", "country": "LU", "summary": "Luxembourg City tour by sightseeing bus", "tour_id": 2, "book_url": "https://live.tourcms.com/reserve/r1.php?t=2&a=12846&w=13407&people=1&ty=t&k=e43ff2cdb3ed", "duration": 1, "end_time": "MULTI", "has_sale": 1, "location": "Luxembourg", "longdesc": "<strong>Step on the immersive Luxembourg City Bus Tour!</strong>\\nImmerse into the beauty of Luxembourg’s capital city and unveil hidden gems and  historical landmarks on board of this sightseeing cozy minibus. The Luxembourg City Bus Tour offers you a convenient and immersive way to discover the rich history, stunning architecture, and vibrant culture of our beautiful green capital during the whole time of the year. Do you wish to see all the highlights in the city? Book your seats now.\\n<strong>About the Luxembourg City Bus Tour</strong>\\nThroughout the tour, you will be provided with informative content with the help of a high-quality and enriching audio guide, sharing historical facts about the city’s past and present. The bus is equipped with comfortable seating, air-conditioning, and large windows, ensuring you’ll have the best view to capture the best pictures. This city bus tour doesn’t include any stops, however it offers an ideal introduction to Luxembourg’s unique blend of old-modern charm and contemporary energy. Whether you’re a first-time visitor or a seasoned traveler, you’ll gain deeper appreciation for our little European gem!", "priority": "MEDIUM", "tour_url": "https://sightseeing.lu/trip/luxembourg-city-bus-tour/", "validity": {"validity_type": "NOT SET", "validity_value": 0, "validity_minutes": 0}, "available": "Check Availability Calendar", "documents": "", "essential": "* Please wait for the driver’s permission before you enter the bus and show him/her your ticket. \\n* This bus tour is not a Hop on Hop off and has no stops included. \\n* Baby strollers and wheelchairs are not allowed in ths bus.  \\n* We don’t take any responsibility on baby strollers", "itinerary": "<strong>Luxembourg City Bus Tour itinerary</strong>\\nUnveil hidden gems and immerse yourself in the captivating beauty of Luxembourg’s capital city with the Luxembourg City Bus Tour. Discover historical landmarks, stunning architecture, and vibrant culture on this convenient and immersive sightseeing experience.  Depart from the Boulevard de la Pétrusse, near Spuerkeess  HQ with our Luxembourg City Bus Tour. Then, you will be driven along the avenue de la Liberte at the Quartier de la Gare. Gare is a simple neighbourhood and a bustling transport hub that encompasses Luxembourg station, near which hotels and chain stores are grouped together.\\n\\nThen, our driver takes you along the Constitution square, where you can marvel the famous Gëlle Fra statue, the remembrance memorial. Among other monuments, you also see the Malakoff Tower, an important monument built as part of the fortress in 1861. This tower has been fully restored and is now the new headquarters of Scouting in Luxembourg asbl. You pass over the Viaduct, also known as Old Bridge.\\n\\nIn just a few seconds, you are entering the city’s business district: Kirchberg. Before that, you will have a chance to see the panoramic elevator and the Pfaffenthal district just before entering the Kirchberg Plateau. Admire the skyscrapers and the splendor of a district rich in architecture. Take a photo of the Luxembourg Philharmonie and don’t miss a visit at the Grand-Duc Jean Museum of Modern Art (Mudam) after your city bus tour", "shortdesc": "Immerse into the beauty of Luxembourg’s capital city and explore the hidden gems on board of our sightseeing cozy minibus. Listen to an audio guide and admire the historic landmarks and architecture as well as the vibrant and modern side of the city", "time_type": "strict", "tour_name": "Luxembourg City Tour", "tour_tags": {"tag": [{"text": "Activity is suitable for adults only", "token": "adults-only", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity is largely centered around animals", "token": "animals", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour is guided by pre-recorded commentary", "token": "audio-guide", "value": 0}, {"text": "Activity visits or happens at a beach", "token": "beaches", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour involves sightseeing by bicycle", "token": "bike-tours", "value": 0}, {"text": "Tour involves sightseeing by boat", "token": "boat-tours